imdb.plot outline: our team of Interior Design and Real Estate experts tackle an assortment of Victoria's design projects. Join the cast, Danisha Drury, Amy McGeachy, Jason Binab and John Byrne, as they utilize their individual talents to tackle the client's challenges. Many considerations will come into play when the team takes action... some of these elements may include design scheme, client's style and taste, existing pieces to be worked into the design, era of the home, neighborhood, resale value, and initial investment. Learn tips from the trades, designers, financial advisers and Realtors on which projects to undergo. Learn where to shop for the products seen in the episodes, viewing some of the newest product on the market.
imdb.title: Design District: The Series
plot: Design and Real Estate experts take on the tasks and challenges of Victoria's residents and business owners. They rise to the challenge and use their own talents and expertise, but not without a little conflict among the team.::Anonymous
